{"tid":1317702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有去新城市請留意！","createTime":"2019-07-14T20:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T21:04:25.000Z","uid":115136,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dec7ffbd998a79459da75aaa9fbed4f2954b12dd","tid":1317702,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:46:18.000Z","msg":"幫推！<br />\n<br />\n如果14/7/19當晚係去食飯，睇戲等消費，有單有據證明，走個陣受傷，可以告鳩新城市。<br />\n以案件Chan Wai Hing v MTR Corp Ltd(DCPI 1649/2015)為例，事發時原告人在拉開商場出入口的玻璃門時因地面濕滑跣倒，導致髖部骨折。原告人向該商場的擁有者，即商場管理者提出民事索償，指意外乃由於商場的擁有者及管理者的疏忽或違反責任所致。"},{"pid":"fcd44fc0057653f52fe02a8c8bec0a927ce0f164","tid":1317702,"uid":33215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"新城市d大陸廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19457f49a767e1d898e55632537226cd040657cf","tid":1317702,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:53:09.000Z","msg":"告9 佢啦"},{"pid":"45fa465a53757be091ea14390be79b5293b1432c","tid":1317702,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe7e7139461ce799506ac14b26a11dd95e298d8","tid":1317702,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T21:04:25.000Z","msg":"推上報"}]}